{"title":"岳阳楼","authors":["顾绍康"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":1,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"岳阳楼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾绍康"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背熟了范学士那篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久负盛名的“楼记”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迁客骚人洞庭荡舟时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总会评说“落霞与孤鹜齐飞”是诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄鹤来去是谜而已"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有这政通人和的遗墨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才为傍水而立的名楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"添了浓重的一笔！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据说老先生并未登临此楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假若他曾来此一览，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或许那楼、那水、那“记”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未必能如此洋洋洒洒命笔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而那“先天下之忧而忧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后天下之乐而乐”的壮怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却给后人为民、为官、为政，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勾勒了一个不该遗忘的命题。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}